    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/1cc7ab727582229781207a0c1b9642ba.poster.avif?t=1767230797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/1cc7ab727582229781207a0c1b9642ba.webm?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/1cc7ab727582229781207a0c1b9642ba.mp4?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A dating sim where you <i>avoid</i> cute babes instead of dating them?!</strong></h2> You are Aya - a new transfer student that wants nothing more than to start fresh in your final year of high school. New school, new people, making friends will DEFINITELY work this time! But it seems like some of your new classmates want more than simple friendship...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/acbf5ceb87445c3ab5d9f90e9f51bb4b.poster.avif?t=1767230797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/acbf5ceb87445c3ab5d9f90e9f51bb4b.webm?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/acbf5ceb87445c3ab5d9f90e9f51bb4b.mp4?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive highschool</strong></h2> You don't want to graduate highschool without a single friend, but become too close with someone and you might cause a misunderstanding! You'll need to balance your affection level in order to avoid getting heartbreak or heartache!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/855f76c741988b32858421b0f58bc7f0.poster.avif?t=1767230797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/855f76c741988b32858421b0f58bc7f0.webm?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/855f76c741988b32858421b0f58bc7f0.mp4?t=1767230797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cutscenes that pop off the page</strong></h2> Watch events play out with professionally hand drawn, animated manga cutscenes!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet your new classmates</strong></h2> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703610/extras/603e03723af310d4a1bdafe7fa95338b.avif?t=1767230797\" width=616 height=958 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play as a non-binary, ace/aro protagonist!<br></li><li>Animated Manga Cutscenes<br></li><li>Make difficult decisions and balance your affection<br></li><li>Multiple unique endings where you date, or befriend each girl, or all of them at the same time! (And more)<br></li><li>Secrets<br></li><li>You can't date a skeleton in this game :(</li></ul>",
